---
title: Chicken Shawarma Plate with Hummus and Seasoned Pita Crisps
description: We've paired up with Sabra Hummus for a classic Middle Eastern shawarma plate. Our Shawarma blend is smoky, sweet and oh so delicious. Paired with pickled cabbage, crispy chickpeas and a bright and zingy tabouli salad! Its equally tasty and colourful!
